dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Kenosha County, WI 2014
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Kenosha County, Wisconsin in 2014. They are feature classes within the geodatabase Kenosha_Hydro_2014.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are 'KENOSHA_HYDROLINE_2014' and 'KENOSHA_HYDROPOLY_2014'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
